FAHDU – Discover, Creator Profile & Wallet Recharge Flow
Discover Page (User Flow)
After login:
Navbar → Third Option → Discover
On the Discover Page, users can:
View multiple creators from different niches
Browse:
 Popular Creators
 New Creators
Scroll and explore different profiles
Users can click on any creator name/profile to open the Creator Profile Page. Creator Profile Page Flow
When a user opens a creator profile, they can see:
 Creator Fee Structure
The creator’s charges for:
Chat
Live Stream
Video Call
Audio Call
The profile may also show:
Different pricing for:
Followers
Subscribers
Follow Feature
A Follow button is visible on the profile page
User clicks Follow
User becomes a follower of that creator
As a follower, the user can:
Send messages
Start chat
Interact based on available wallet balance
Wallet & Recharge Flow
To chat or subscribe, users must have sufficient coins.
If balance is low:
Step 1: Open Wallet
Go to Home Page
Click Top Hamburger Icon
Select Wallet
